        },
        {
          "title": "The Beyond",
          "year": 1981,
          "note": "No. 2. Fulci's hotel over a portal to hell; eye horror and gloriously analog dread."
        },
        {
          "title": "Re-Animator",
          "year": 1985,
          "note": "No. 4. Shared with Adam's list."
